Super  Moose  the  defender  of  justice  and   the
protector of innocent. And collector of apples. Did
I  mentioned  wild  berries?  Here's  a  cartoonish
adventure game where you'll be playing as  a  moose
that puts on a cape and wants to rescue the animals
of the forest. Along the way there will be lots  of
goodies so make sure you collect them in  order  to
increase your score. Dangers lurk in the forest  so
keep your eyes open. Falling rocks, rolling logs or
even bear traps will diminish your health.

1- Unpack, burn or mount
2- Install the game
3- Go To Hell!

NOTE:
Source is retail. Witcher 3 got  delayed,  so  this
is the best what polish developers  have  to  offer
this year. This game is a real "masterpiece".
